Package org.bukkit

Interface Art

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<Art>, Keyed, Keyed, OldEnum<Art>
public interface Art extends OldEnum<Art>, Keyed
Represents the art on a painting.

The arts listed in this interface are present in the default server or can be enabled via a FeatureFlag. There may be additional arts present in the server, for example from a Datapack which can be accessed via RegistryAccess.registryAccess() and RegistryKey.PAINTING_VARIANT.
